title: [Whistler's Pass]
description: A faint scratching and rustling sound emanates from within some of the many small, grass-filled nests dotting the high stone walls.  Although the sound's exact source remains lost within the darkness of night, it is obvious that many small yet unseen creatures survive in this dry, cold environment.
